{"tid":1099718,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"小米去年賺 134 億人民幣，雷軍年薪獨占 98 億","createTime":"2019-04-10T03:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T05:34:06.000Z","uid":186087,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d80d6e4435ca35c7a052e0043dbdec99ea3840cf","tid":1099718,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T03:10:30.000Z","msg":"鐘意曬自己人工,層樓幾靚ge 朋友,唔該同雷軍比較。人地1年人工夠買起成個區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小米去年營收為 1749.15 億人民幣，且終於轉虧為盈賺了 134.78 億元，約新台幣 619 億元。但小米財報發布當日股價收 11.75 港元，跌 0.68%，年初至今跌近一成，市值蒸發約 102.93 億港元，約 404 億台幣，而與上市相較縮水近 31%。<br />\n<br />\n不過據香港《明報》報導，集團中 5 名最高薪酬人士的年薪合計就高達 102.18 億人民幣，年成長 51 倍，當然最高薪員工不出所料就是小米董事長雷軍，一人薪酬就占了近百億人民幣。據調查，去年雷軍獲發一批小米 B 股做為薪酬，估計約 98.27 億元，帶動員工福利開支激增至 3.23 倍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/blog.moneydj.com/news/2019/04/09/%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B3%25BA-134-%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25EF%25BC%258C%25E9%259B%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2596%25AA%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%258D%25A0-98-%25E5%2584%2584/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fblog.moneydj.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2F04%2F09%2F%2525E5%2525B0%25258F%2525E7%2525B1%2525B3%2525E5%25258E%2525BB%2525E5%2525B9%2525B4%2525E8%2525B3%2525BA-134-%2525E5%252584%252584%2525E4%2525BA%2525BA%2525E6%2525B0%252591%2525E5%2525B9%2525A3%2525EF%2525BC%25258C%2525E9%25259B%2525B7%2525E8%2525BB%25258D%2525E5%2525B9%2525B4%2525E8%252596%2525AA%2525E7%25258D%2525A8%2525E5%25258D%2525A0-98-%2525E5%252584%252584%2Famp%2F&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIvFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=8ca05dc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/blog.moneydj.com/news/2019/04/09/%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B3%25BA-134-%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3%25EF%25BC%258C%25E9%259B%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2596